\c 23
\s Abangavunyelwayo ukungena ebandleni leN\nd kosi\nd*
\p
\v 1 Olimele emasendeni, loba oqunywe amaphambili, angangeni ebandleni leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 2 Ozelwe ngobufebe angangeni ebandleni leN\nd kosi\nd*; ngitsho isizukulwana sakhe setshumi kasiyikungena ebandleni leN\nd kosi\x + Zek. 9.6.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 3 UmAmoni lomMowabi kangangeni ebandleni leN\nd kosi\nd*; ngitsho isizukulwana sabo setshumi kasiyikungena ebandleni leN\nd kosi\nd*, kuze kube laphakade\x + Neh. 13.1,2.\x*;
\v 4 ngenxa yokuthi kabalihlangabezanga endleleni ngesinkwa langamanzi ekuphumeni kwenu eGibhithe\x + 2.29.\x*; futhi ngoba baqhatsha ukumelana lawe uBalami indodana kaBeyori owePethori oweMesopotamiya ukuze akuqalekise\x + Nani 22.5,6. 2 Pet. 2.15.\x*.
\v 5 Kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho kayifunanga ukuzwa uBalami; kodwa iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yaphendula isiqalekiso saba yisibusiso kuwe, ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho yakuthanda\x + Nani 23.11.\x*.
\v 6 Kawuyikudinga ukuthula kwabo lokuhle kwabo zonke izinsuku zakho, kuze kube laphakade\x + Ezra 9.12.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Unganengwa ngumEdoma, ngoba ungumfowenu; unganengwa ngumGibhithe\x + Gen. 25.24-26. Obad. 10,12.\x*, ngoba wawungowemzini elizweni lakhe\x + Eks. 22.21; 23.9. Levi 19.34. Dute. 10.19.\x*.
\v 8 Abantwana abazalwa yibo, besizukulwana sesithathu sabo, bangangena ebandleni leN\nd kosi\nd*.
\s Ukuhlambuluka kwamathente
\p
\v 9 Lapho inkamba iphuma ukuyamelana lezitha zakho, uzazigcina kuyo yonke into embi.
\p
\v 10 Uba ekhona phakathi kwenu umuntu ongahlambulukanga ngenxa yokungcola okwehla ebusuku, uzaphumela ngaphandle kwenkamba, angangeni phakathi kwenkamba\x + Levi 15.16.\x*.
\v 11 Kodwa kuzakuthi sekuzakuhlwa uzageza ngamanzi, lalapho ilanga selitshonile angene aye phakathi kwenkamba\x + Levi 15.5.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Njalo uzakuba lendawo ngaphandle kwenkamba lapho ozaphumela khona ukuya ngaphandle\x + Nani 2.17.\x*,
\v 13 ube lesikhonkwane ezikhalini zakho; njalo kuzakuthi usuye\f + \fk usuye: \fl Heb. \fq usuhlezi.\f* ngaphandle, ugebhe ngaso, uphenduke ugqibele okuphume kuwe.
\v 14 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho iyahamba phakathi kwenkamba yakho, ukukukhulula\x + Levi 26.12.\x*, lokunikela izitha zakho phambi kwakho. Ngakho inkamba yakho izakuba ngcwele, ukuze ingaboni lutho oluyangisayo phakathi kwakho, ikufulathele\x + 7.2,23.\x*.
\s Imilayo emayelana lezigqili, lamawule, lomvuzo
\p
\v 15 Unganikeli enkosini yaso isigqili esibalekele kuwe sisuka enkosini yaso\x + 1 Sam. 30.15.\x*;
\v 16 sizahlala lawe phakathi kwakho, endaweni esizayikhetha, kwelinye lamasango akho, lapho okusilungele khona; ungasicindezeli\x + Eks. 22.21.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Kakungabi khona iwule elethempeli phakathi kwamadodakazi akoIsrayeli\x + Levi 19.29.\x*, njalo kakungabi khona inkotshana phakathi kwamadodana akoIsrayeli\x + 1 Kho. 14.24. 15.12. 22.46. 2 Kho. 23.7.\x*.
\v 18 Ungalethi iholo lewule lemali yenja endlini yeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ngokwaloba yisiphi isithembiso; ngoba lokho kokubili kuyisinengiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho.
\p
\v 19 Ungeboleki umfowenu ngenzalo, inzalo yemali, inzalo yokudla, inzalo yaloba yiyiphi into ebolekwa ngenzalo\x + Eks. 22.25. Luka 6.34,35.\x*.
\v 20 Ungeboleka owezizweni ngenzalo, kodwa ungeboleki umfowenu ngenzalo\x + 15.3.\x*, ukuze iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ikubusise kukho konke\x + 15.10.\x* ofaka isandla sakho kukho elizweni oya kulo ukudla ilifa lalo\x + 12.7.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Nxa uthembisa isithembiso eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho, ungaphuzi ukusikhokha; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izasibiza lokusibiza kuwe; njalo kuzakuba yisono kuwe\x + Nani 30.2. Hlab. 66.13,14. 76.11.\x*.
\v 22 Kodwa uba uyekela ukuthembisa, kakuyikuba yisono kuwe.
\v 23 Lokho okuphuma endebeni zakho uzakugcina ukwenze; njengokuthembisa kwakho eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho, umnikelo wesihle owukhulume ngomlomo wakho.
\p
\v 24 Nxa ungena esivinini somakhelwane wakho, ungadla izithelo zevini njengokuthanda kwakho usuthe; kodwa ungafaki \add lutho\add* esitsheni sakho.
\v 25 Nxa ungena emabeleni amileyo kamakhelwane wakho\x + 16.9.\x*, ungakha izikhwebu ngesandla sakho; kodwa ungangenisi isikela emabeleni amileyo\x + 16.9.\x* kamakhelwane wakho\x + Nani 30.2. Hlab. 66.13,14. 76.11.\x*.
